Package twitter4j.examples.list

example codes for list resources

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CreateUserList
    Creates a public list.
    CreateUserListMember
    Adds a user to a specified list.
    CreateUserListMembers
    Adds multiple users to a specified list.
    CreateUserListSubscription
    Subscribes specified list.
    DeleteUserListMember
    Deletes a user from a list.
    DestroyUserList
    Destroys a specified list.
    DestroyUserListSubscription
    Unsubscribes specified list.
    GetUserListMembers
    Lists list members.
    GetUserListMemberships
    List the lists the specified user has been added to.
    GetUserLists
    List the lists of the specified user.
    GetUserListStatuses
    Show tweet timeline for members of the specified list.
    GetUserListSubscribers
    Lists list subscribers.
    GetUserListSubscriptions
    List the lists the specified user follows.
    ShowUserList
    Show the specified list.
    ShowUserListMembership
    Checks list membership.
    ShowUserListSubscription
    Checks list subscription.
    UpdateUserList
    Updates the specified list.
